My eerste HTML code ek sal die CSS wat ek by dit skryf in new Files sit sodat die
progress gelog word in verskillende files.

<!DOCTYPE html> <!- document type, and help the browser display web page correctly, is not case sensitive (before any HTML tags)
                    declaration for HTML5 -->

<html> <!- is the root element of an HTML page -->
<head> <!- contains meta (Tab Display ) information about the HTML page -->
<title>First HTML</title> <!- Displays the Title on Tab -->
</head> <!- end of (Tab Display ) information about the HTML page -->
<body> <!- defines the document's body, and is a container for all the visible contents, 
           such as headings, paragraphs, images, hyperlinks, tables, lists, etc. -->

<h1>Welcome to my first HTML Design</h1> <!- defines a large heading -->

<p>This is the first HTML page i am creating, there is lots of interesting things to do,<br>
HTML is used to create web pages and define the structure of the page.</p> <!- defines a paragraph -->

<p>Using CSS in HTML can advance the look of our page and give it more life.</p> <!- defines a paragraph -->

</body> <!- end of the document's body, that displays all the visible contents -->
</html> <!- end of elements in a HTML page -->
